<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Irium Mining Guide</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/style.css">
    <style>
        .mining-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background: rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid #ffa500;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        .warning-box h3 {
            color: #ffa500;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .code-block {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: monospace;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .step {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
        }
        .step h4 {
            color: #0066cc;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="nav">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/" class="nav-logo">
                <img src="https://www.iriumlabs.org/logo.svg" alt="Irium" class="nav-logo-img">
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/" class="nav-link">HOME</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/about.html" class="nav-link">ABOUT</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/features.html" class="nav-link">FEATURES</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/specs.html" class="nav-link">SPECS</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/whitepaper.html" class="nav-link">WHITEPAPER</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/explorer/" class="nav-link">EXPLORER</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/dashboard/" class="nav-link">DASHBOARD</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/wallet/" class="nav-link">WALLET</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://www.iriumlabs.org/support.html" class="nav-link">SUPPORT</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="mining-container">
        <h1>⛏️ Irium Mining Guide</h1>
        
        <div class="warning-box">
            <h3>⚠️ Important: Individual Mining Setup Required</h3>
            <p><strong>Current Issue:</strong> All miners are using the same wallet address, meaning all mining rewards go to one address instead of individual miners.</p>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Each miner must use their own individual wallet to receive their own mining rewards.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h4>Step 1: Fix Current Mining Setup</h4>
            <p>If you're currently mining, stop the old miners and set up individual wallets:</p>
            <div class="code-block">
# Stop current miners
pkill -f irium-simple-miner.py

# Run the migration script
./scripts/fix-mining-setup.sh
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h4>Step 2: Create Your Individual Miner</h4>
            <p>Create a new miner with your own wallet:</p>
            <div class="code-block">
# Create a new miner wallet
./scripts/setup-miner.sh my-miner-$(whoami)

# This will create:
# - ~/.irium-miners/my-miner-$(whoami)/irium-wallet.json
# - Your unique mining address
# - Miner configuration
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h4>Step 3: Start Mining with Your Wallet</h4>
            <p>Start mining using your individual wallet:</p>
            <div class="code-block">
# Method 1: Using wallet file
python3 scripts/irium-miner-individual.py --wallet ~/.irium-miners/my-miner-$(whoami)/irium-wallet.json

# Method 2: Using miner ID
python3 scripts/irium-miner-individual.py --miner-id my-miner-$(whoami)
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h4>Step 4: Verify Your Mining Address</h4>
            <p>Check that you're mining to your own address:</p>
            <div class="code-block">
# Check your mining address
cat ~/.irium-miners/my-miner-$(whoami)/irium-wallet.json | grep -A 1 "addresses"
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>🔧 Advanced Configuration</h2>
        
        <div class="step">
            <h4>Multiple Miners on Same Machine</h4>
            <p>If running multiple miners on the same machine, use different ports:</p>
            <div class="code-block">
# Miner 1
python3 scripts/irium-miner-individual.py --miner-id miner-1 --port 38292

# Miner 2  
python3 scripts/irium-miner-individual.py --miner-id miner-2 --port 38293
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h4>Mining Pool Setup</h4>
            <p>For mining pools, each pool participant should have their own wallet:</p>
            <div class="code-block">
# Pool participant 1
./scripts/setup-miner.sh pool-participant-1
python3 scripts/irium-miner-individual.py --miner-id pool-participant-1

# Pool participant 2
./scripts/setup-miner.sh pool-participant-2  
python3 scripts/irium-miner-individual.py --miner-id pool-participant-2
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>✅ Benefits of Individual Mining</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ <strong>Fair Rewards:</strong> Each miner gets their own mining rewards</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Security:</strong> No shared wallet files</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Decentralization:</strong> Better distribution of mining power</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Transparency:</strong> Clear ownership of mining rewards</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Scalability:</strong> Easy to add new miners</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>🚨 Troubleshooting</h2>
        
        <div class="step">
            <h4>Wallet file not found</h4>
            <p>Make sure you ran the setup script first:</p>
            <div class="code-block">./scripts/setup-miner.sh my-miner-name</div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h4>Permission denied</h4>
            <p>Make sure scripts are executable:</p>
            <div class="code-block">
chmod +x scripts/setup-miner.sh
chmod +x scripts/irium-miner-individual.py
chmod +x scripts/fix-mining-setup.sh
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h4>Still mining to wrong address</h4>
            <p>Check your wallet file and restart the miner:</p>
            <div class="code-block">
# Check wallet content
cat ~/.irium-miners/my-miner-*/irium-wallet.json

# Restart miner
pkill -f irium-miner-individual.py
python3 scripts/irium-miner-individual.py --miner-id my-miner-name
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  <section class="section" style="padding:60px 0 20px;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Quick Mining (v1.0)</h2>
      <p class="muted">Full P2P miner (single and multicore). No hardcoded wallets — miners use their own wallet via env/CLI.</p>
      <h3>Install Dependencies</h3>
      <pre><code>pip3 install --user pycryptodome qrcode pillow</code></pre>
      <h3>Create Wallet</h3>
      <pre><code>python3 scripts/irium-wallet-proper.py create
python3 scripts/irium-wallet-proper.py new-address</code></pre>
      <h3>Start Node</h3>
      <pre><code>nohup python3 -u scripts/irium-node.py 38291 > /tmp/node.log 2>&1 &</code></pre>
      <pre><code>sudo systemctl start irium-node
sudo systemctl enable irium-node
sudo journalctl -u irium-node -f</code></pre>
      <h3>Single Miner (Full P2P)</h3>
      <pre><code>export IRIUM_WALLET_FILE="$HOME/.irium/irium-wallet.json"
nohup python3 -u scripts/irium-node.py 38291 > /tmp/node.log 2>&1 &
python3 scripts/irium-miner.py 38292</code></pre>
      <h3>Multicore (Full P2P)</h3>
      <pre><code>export IRIUM_WALLET_FILE="$HOME/.irium/irium-wallet.json"
nohup python3 -u scripts/irium-node.py 38291 > /tmp/node.log 2>&1 &
bash scripts/irium-miner-multicore.sh 4
./scripts/tail-mining-logs.sh 4 38292</code></pre>
      <h3>APIs</h3>
      <p>Base: <a href="https://api.iriumlabs.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://api.iriumlabs.org/</a></p>
      <pre><code>curl https://api.iriumlabs.org/api/stats
curl https://api.iriumlabs.org/api/block/1
curl "https://api.iriumlabs.org/api/blocks?limit=10"</code></pre>
      <p style="margin-top:12px" class="muted">
        Docs: <a href="https://github.com/iriumlabs/irium/blob/main/QUICKSTART.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Quickstart</a> ·
        <a href="https://github.com/iriumlabs/irium/blob/main/MINING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mining</a> ·
        <a href="https://github.com/iriumlabs/irium/releases/tag/v1.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Release v1.0</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

